ParallelChunk.en:
The problem of ageing is one which we all share; 
          and
         we should approach this with some dignity.

European standards, particularly for food production and the manufacture of clothes and toys, are the best in the world; 
          but
         these high standards add costs and make production inside EU borders more expensive.

ParallelChunk.fr:
Les normes européennes sont les meilleures du monde, notamment en ce qui concerne les denrées alimentaires, les vêtements et les jouets; 
          mais
         ces contraintes renchérissent les coûts de production à l'intérieur de l'Union européenne.
